Package service.impl

Class SimpleCache

java.lang.Object
service.impl.SimpleCache
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cache
public class SimpleCache
extends java.lang.Object
implements Cache
Class SimpleCache Simple implementation of Cache allow to store data by key-value pairs. NullPointerException safe, allows null keys and values. There is no timeout, so caches persist as long as SimpleCache exists or until clean () methods are called. Logs stored into ./log/ directory.
Version:
1.0.0 created on 20.07.2021
Author:
Oleksandr Storozhuk
